## 2. Client Component Import Boundary

Client Components may only import:

- Client-safe UI primitives (`#components/ui/*`, `#components/nexus/*`)
- Client-safe hooks (`#hooks/*`)
- Shared types and constants (no `server-only` transitive imports)
- Designated client barrels: `#features/<module>/client`

```tsx
// ❌ imports server barrel from a Client Component — pulls server-only into the client bundle
import { listContacts } from '#features/contacts';

// ✅ use the explicit client barrel
import { archiveContactAction } from '#features/contacts/client';
```

Client Components must not import feature `index.ts` barrels unless the barrel is explicitly verified as client-safe (no `server-only`, no DB, no `next/headers`).

